SubjectRegulations Amending the Employment Insurance Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS in order to temporarily waive the EI waiting period to ease the financial pressure when eligible individuals seek EI benefits during the ongoing COVID-19 pandemic.
